1
00:00:03,671 --> 00:00:05,924
<i>Within the spreading darkness</i>

2
00:00:06,007 --> 00:00:08,676
<i>I pledged a vow to the revolution</i>

3
00:00:08,801 --> 00:00:13,806
<i>I can't let anybody interrupt it</i>

4
00:00:13,890 --> 00:00:18,978
<i>I'm going to change</i>

5
00:00:27,445 --> 00:00:31,699
<i>The future that
the forbidden fruit foretells...</i>

6
00:00:31,783 --> 00:00:35,787
<i>I'm going to change</i>

7
00:00:35,870 --> 00:00:40,166
<i>The dream into reality</i>

8
00:00:42,794 --> 00:00:48,800
<i>The ending</i>

9
00:00:48,883 --> 00:00:52,053
<i>That everybody wants</i>

10
00:00:53,012 --> 00:00:55,306
<i>Within the spreading darkness</i>

11
00:00:55,390 --> 00:00:58,059
<i>I pledged our vow to the revolution</i>

12
00:00:58,142 --> 00:01:02,939
<i>I can't let anybody interrupt it</i>

13
00:01:03,106 --> 00:01:08,319
<i>Someday I'll show you</i>

14
00:01:08,486 --> 00:01:11,698
<i>A bright and ideal</i>

15
00:01:11,781 --> 00:01:17,745
<i>World</i>

16
00:01:27,755 --> 00:01:30,341
FRIEND

17
00:01:36,514 --> 00:01:37,599
I understand...

18
00:01:38,182 --> 00:01:41,019
I can't be your boyfriend,
but I can play the part...

19
00:01:42,604 --> 00:01:46,649
Thank you...
I'll work hard to make you love me.

20
00:01:48,526 --> 00:01:52,405
<i>I'll have her meet L to find out
his name</i>

21
00:01:52,488 --> 00:01:54,866
<i>and eliminate
the entire task force HQ</i>

22
00:01:55,491 --> 00:01:57,452
<i>I'll kill her afterwards...</i>

23
00:01:58,369 --> 00:01:59,412
<i>That's right.</i>

24
00:01:59,537 --> 00:02:03,249
<i>She's the only person who knows
Kira's identity.</i>

25
00:02:03,875 --> 00:02:06,210
<i>I can't let her live for long.</i>

26
00:02:06,878 --> 00:02:08,630
So you'll just act
like my boyfriend, huh?

27
00:02:08,713 --> 00:02:10,048
That's a good start.

28
00:02:10,715 --> 00:02:14,552
So then, could you show me
your Shinigami?

29
00:02:15,678 --> 00:02:17,722
<i>I suppose it's necessary
to make her trust me...</i>

30
00:02:18,556 --> 00:02:19,724
Yeah. All right.

31
00:02:20,475 --> 00:02:21,851
Could you turn around?

32
00:02:21,934 --> 00:02:22,935
Okay.

33
00:02:30,234 --> 00:02:31,361
You can turn around now.

34
00:02:31,569 --> 00:02:32,695
Okay.

35
00:02:34,572 --> 00:02:35,573
Hi!

36
00:02:36,115 --> 00:02:37,283
Ooh...

37
00:02:37,408 --> 00:02:40,662
He's a completely different type
of Shinigami from Rem, isn't he?

38
00:02:40,745 --> 00:02:42,789
I already know your name. Ryuk.

39
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:44,082
Pleased to meet you!

40
00:02:44,374 --> 00:02:45,416
Yeah, pleased to meet you.

41
00:02:46,626 --> 00:02:49,754
Oh yeah, Light, do you know
how to kill a Shinigami?

42
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,715
You're already calling me
by my first name?

43
00:02:53,091 --> 00:02:56,094
Then could I call you "Knight" instead?

44
00:02:56,177 --> 00:02:58,763
Because you're like Misa's knight
in shining armor!

45
00:02:59,263 --> 00:03:00,348
Light is fine.

46
00:03:01,766 --> 00:03:04,894
Are you planning to check all
the videos of Aoyama

47
00:03:04,977 --> 00:03:06,729
on the 22nd by yourself?

48
00:03:07,271 --> 00:03:08,314
Yes.

49
00:03:08,398 --> 00:03:09,649
It is very likely that Kira
and the Second Kira

50
00:03:09,732 --> 00:03:12,360
made contact with each other there
on that day.

51
00:03:12,819 --> 00:03:14,737
I want to check them all.

52
00:03:15,780 --> 00:03:16,906
Also, Mr. Yagami...

53
00:03:17,031 --> 00:03:18,199
Yes?

54
00:03:18,491 --> 00:03:22,120
I would like Mr. Mogi to keep
watch over Light's activities.

55
00:03:22,578 --> 00:03:23,955
"Light's activities?"

56
00:03:24,539 --> 00:03:29,210
In the event that Light is Kira,
the Second Kira might try to contact him...

57
00:03:29,419 --> 00:03:30,670
...in some way.

58
00:03:31,921 --> 00:03:32,922
I understand.

59
00:03:34,424 --> 00:03:36,968
So when does Ryuzaki sleep?

60
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:40,638
I saw him sleeping in that
exact same position the other day.

61
00:03:42,473 --> 00:03:43,850
No, I'm serious...

62
00:03:46,811 --> 00:03:49,188
So when a Shinigami has feelings
for a certain person...

63
00:03:49,731 --> 00:03:53,484
and kills someone in order to
extend that person's life,

64
00:03:53,568 --> 00:03:55,194
the Shinigami dies, huh?

65
00:03:55,695 --> 00:03:56,696
Yes.

66
00:03:59,031 --> 00:04:01,951
I can't imagine there's
a Shinigami who would do that.

67
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:06,372
That's right. It doesn't seem like
the kind of thing that you would do.

68
00:04:06,914 --> 00:04:09,792
By the way, from where have you
been sending your tapes

69
00:04:09,876 --> 00:04:11,127
to the television stations?

70
00:04:11,711 --> 00:04:15,381
Umm. .. The first time was Osaka.
Then it was Tokyo.

71
00:04:15,673 --> 00:04:17,258
This other time was from Nagano.

72
00:04:17,341 --> 00:04:21,220
I used the Bullet Train so
my location couldn't be pinpointed.

73
00:04:21,804 --> 00:04:23,806
So you still have videotapes
and envelopes

74
00:04:23,890 --> 00:04:26,768
with your friend's fingerprints
on them, right?

75
00:04:26,851 --> 00:04:27,894
Yeah.

76
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:31,647
Then you should dispose of
everything used to create the videos...

77
00:04:32,815 --> 00:04:37,695
But only after sending one last video
from another location tomorrow...

78
00:04:38,404 --> 00:04:39,489
You should say...

79
00:04:40,698 --> 00:04:43,075
"I will stop trying to meet Kira."

80
00:04:43,367 --> 00:04:46,537
"I'd like to thank the police
for their advice."

81
00:04:47,246 --> 00:04:51,042
"But I'm going to help Kira
erase evil from the world."

82
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:54,587
"I'm going to cooperate with him
and gain his acceptance."

83
00:04:55,797 --> 00:05:00,718
"I will begin by punishing criminals
that Kira hasn't punished yet. Also. .

84
00:05:01,594 --> 00:05:04,138
"I plan to make this world
a better place"

85
00:05:04,222 --> 00:05:08,684
"by sharing this power
among those who are worthy."

86
00:05:09,185 --> 00:05:10,686
"Share the power?"

87
00:05:11,312 --> 00:05:13,481
It's a line to throw off
the investigation.

88
00:05:13,773 --> 00:05:16,567
There are already two people
with this power.

89
00:05:16,776 --> 00:05:19,070
It's not too far of a stretch
that there may be more.

90
00:05:19,153 --> 00:05:21,739
And if they believe that they'll multiply,
it will create panic.

91
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,282
Can you do it?

92
00:05:23,449 --> 00:05:26,077
You don't have to ask.
Just tell me to do it.

93
00:05:26,452 --> 00:05:28,788
I'll do whatever you say.

94
00:05:29,330 --> 00:05:31,332
Also, one more important thing.

95
00:05:31,415 --> 00:05:32,416
Okay!

96
00:05:32,667 --> 00:05:34,794
If you're caught by the police...

97
00:05:34,961 --> 00:05:37,255
if you're arrested as a suspect,

98
00:05:37,338 --> 00:05:40,258
don't say anything about us
or the notebook.

99
00:05:40,716 --> 00:05:41,717
There's no proof against you

100
00:05:41,801 --> 00:05:44,136
as long as they don't get
a hold of the notebook and verify it.

101
00:05:45,221 --> 00:05:46,848
Can you promise to do that?

102
00:05:47,348 --> 00:05:48,432
I promise!

103
00:05:48,766 --> 00:05:51,978
So then, we're officially boyfriend
and girlfriend, right?

104
00:05:52,645 --> 00:05:54,021
Well, I guess so.

105
00:05:54,689 --> 00:05:56,232
Now for my conditions.

106
00:05:56,816 --> 00:05:58,943
Go on a date with me
at least once a week.

107
00:06:00,361 --> 00:06:02,530
<i>She really doesn't get it...</i>

108
00:06:02,905 --> 00:06:03,906
That's impossible.

109
00:06:04,073 --> 00:06:05,533
W-Why?

110
00:06:06,033 --> 00:06:08,452
It doesn't seem like
you'll understand unless I tell you.

111
00:06:08,703 --> 00:06:11,747
I already suspects that I'm Kira.

112
00:06:12,123 --> 00:06:15,543
What? L's pretty amazing...

113
00:06:15,918 --> 00:06:17,044
Everyone's saying that

114
00:06:17,128 --> 00:06:20,423
he doesn't understand or...
that he's stupid.

115
00:06:20,965 --> 00:06:22,592
So he's actually figured out
that much...

116
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:27,680
But thanks to that,
I've also been able to get close to L.

117
00:06:28,222 --> 00:06:31,058
Huh? I and Kira are
in contact with each other?

118
00:06:31,642 --> 00:06:35,771
You're both amazing.
It's making me kind of excited.

119
00:06:36,188 --> 00:06:37,940
Even if I'm Kira,

120
00:06:38,024 --> 00:06:40,610
I thinks he's safe as long as
he hides his name.

121
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:43,905
He came out and told me he was L
in order to directly investigate me.

122
00:06:46,407 --> 00:06:48,576
But he's only positive because

123
00:06:48,659 --> 00:06:51,746
there isn't anyone else
who could possibly be Kira.

124
00:06:52,496 --> 00:06:53,831
And if I play it right,

125
00:06:53,915 --> 00:06:57,960
he'll trust me and
we'll investigate together.

126
00:06:58,377 --> 00:07:02,632
So all you have to do is
take me to where L is, right?

127
00:07:03,174 --> 00:07:04,884
It's not that simple.

128
00:07:05,384 --> 00:07:08,596
It was difficult enough
for me to get close to him.

129
00:07:09,347 --> 00:07:11,140
Besides, if suddenly,

130
00:07:11,223 --> 00:07:13,100
someone close to me
steps into the picture,

131
00:07:13,184 --> 00:07:17,021
and the actions of Kira and
the Second Kira change...

132
00:07:17,772 --> 00:07:20,191
that person will be suspected
of being the Second Kira,

133
00:07:20,274 --> 00:07:23,653
and I'll end up casting
more suspicion on myself.

134
00:07:24,487 --> 00:07:26,197
It would be bad if we get together,

135
00:07:26,447 --> 00:07:29,617
and he makes the connection
that we're intimate...

136
00:07:30,076 --> 00:07:31,410
Do you understand
what I'm trying to say?

137
00:07:31,911 --> 00:07:35,957
Kind of... So does that mean
we can't go on dates?

138
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:39,251
We can't meet in public because
you're afraid that he'll suspect you more?

139
00:07:39,418 --> 00:07:40,461
No.

140
00:07:40,544 --> 00:07:43,464
We should take some time
to think of a plan

141
00:07:43,547 --> 00:07:46,467
so that you can see L
without him knowing about you.

142
00:07:46,634 --> 00:07:47,635
Yeah.

143
00:07:48,219 --> 00:07:50,221
I need you
in order to eliminate L.

144
00:07:50,471 --> 00:07:53,474
I want to be able to keep
in direct contact with you.

145
00:07:53,724 --> 00:07:55,017
Thank goodness...

146
00:07:55,142 --> 00:07:56,185
So...

147
00:07:56,644 --> 00:07:59,146
In order to make sure that
our meetings don't stand out,

148
00:07:59,230 --> 00:08:01,732
I'm going to see other girls.

149
00:08:02,024 --> 00:08:05,778
Huh? What do you mean by that?
You're going to date other girls?

150
00:08:06,195 --> 00:08:07,530
Well, pretty much...

151
00:08:07,655 --> 00:08:08,698
No way!

152
00:08:11,409 --> 00:08:14,245
If I see you with another girl,
I'll kill her.

153
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:16,080
Scary. . .!

154
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:18,082
Listen, Misa sweetie...

155
00:08:18,708 --> 00:08:19,750
"Sweetie," huh?

156
00:08:20,292 --> 00:08:21,585
This isn't a game...

157
00:08:21,919 --> 00:08:25,047
We're both risking our lives
to change the world, aren't we?

158
00:08:25,881 --> 00:08:30,136
Yeah, but...
I love you more. . .than the world...

159
00:08:30,928 --> 00:08:32,221
What are you talking about?

160
00:08:32,555 --> 00:08:36,100
I thought your feelings towards me
were those of just a Kira admirer.

161
00:08:36,767 --> 00:08:39,311
Besides...
This is the first time we've met.

162
00:08:39,979 --> 00:08:41,772
Haven't you ever experienced
love at first sight?

163
00:08:42,023 --> 00:08:43,024
Never...

164
00:08:43,315 --> 00:08:48,863
Well, yes, I wanted to meet Kira out of
gratitude and approval, not out of love.

165
00:08:49,321 --> 00:08:51,949
But, when I first laid eyes on you...

166
00:08:52,158 --> 00:08:53,951
<i>What's with this girl?</i>

167
00:08:54,452 --> 00:08:56,412
Popular as usual...

168
00:08:57,121 --> 00:09:00,082
Then if you love me,
you'll obey me.

169
00:09:00,791 --> 00:09:03,044
You told me before that
you didn't mind being used

170
00:09:03,127 --> 00:09:05,588
and just earlier, you insisted that
you'd do as I say, right?

171
00:09:05,963 --> 00:09:09,467
But I won't allow you to
date other girls.

172
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:11,635
Those are two different things.

173
00:09:12,470 --> 00:09:15,306
I have both notebooks.

174
00:09:15,973 --> 00:09:18,434
If you won't obey, I'll kill you...

175
00:09:18,684 --> 00:09:22,313
I won't let you do that,
Light Yagami.

176
00:09:23,022 --> 00:09:29,570
If you try to kill her,
I'll write your name in my notebook...

177
00:09:29,945 --> 00:09:31,489
And kill you.

178
00:09:32,907 --> 00:09:35,993
I can see her lifespan.

179
00:09:36,827 --> 00:09:41,999
If she dies before that date,
I'll assume that you killed her.

180
00:09:42,583 --> 00:09:46,670
Wouldn't you die if you
used your notebook to save her?

181
00:09:47,254 --> 00:09:49,840
That's right! Then you'll die, Rem!

182
00:09:50,591 --> 00:09:52,093
That's true...

183
00:09:52,635 --> 00:09:55,179
But I don't care.

184
00:09:56,347 --> 00:10:00,935
<i>Is this Shinigami serious?
Then that means, from now on...</i>

185
00:10:02,061 --> 00:10:03,104
Light?

186
00:10:04,688 --> 00:10:06,190
What is it, Mom?

187
00:10:07,525 --> 00:10:09,110
It's already 11:30.

188
00:10:09,276 --> 00:10:11,529
It's not nice to have
a girl stay out so late...

189
00:10:12,196 --> 00:10:13,614
Yeah, you're right.

190
00:10:13,864 --> 00:10:15,157
We ended up having
a long conversation...

191
00:10:15,866 --> 00:10:17,827
Sorry, Mrs. Yagami.

192
00:10:19,995 --> 00:10:22,706
I'm sorry for staying so late.

193
00:10:23,124 --> 00:10:24,708
Light, see you later.

194
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:25,751
Yeah.

195
00:10:25,793 --> 00:10:28,462
Light, walk her to the station.

196
00:10:30,047 --> 00:10:32,174
<i>It won't be good to walk
outside with her now...</i>

197
00:10:33,759 --> 00:10:36,387
It's all right! Good night!

198
00:10:40,432 --> 00:10:41,725
She's cute.

199
00:10:42,101 --> 00:10:46,730
Oh yeah. I was a bit worried at first,
but she sure is cute.

200
00:10:46,897 --> 00:10:47,982
I like her!

201
00:10:48,065 --> 00:10:50,860
<i>That Shinigami is going
to kill me if I kill the girl?</i>

202
00:10:51,402 --> 00:10:54,738
<i>Does that mean I have to deal
with her until she dies?</i>

203
00:10:55,531 --> 00:10:56,657
<i>Not just that,</i>

204
00:10:56,740 --> 00:11:01,537
<i>I'm forced to protect her so
she doesn't get caught by the police.</i>

205
00:11:04,331 --> 00:11:08,586
Thanks to you,
Light really became my knight.

206
00:11:08,836 --> 00:11:10,087
So <i>it seems.</i>

207
00:11:12,464 --> 00:11:14,967
But don't kill him for real, okay?

208
00:11:28,981 --> 00:11:30,733
<i>In order to kill a Shinigami,</i>

209
00:11:30,816 --> 00:11:32,735
<i>that Shinigami
has to use the Death Note</i>

210
00:11:32,818 --> 00:11:36,572
<i>to save a human's life that
it has fallen in love with...</i>

211
00:11:37,907 --> 00:11:41,493
<i>I can't kill Rem
by using the Death Note</i>

212
00:11:41,577 --> 00:11:44,496
<i>to control someone to attack Misa...</i>

213
00:11:45,414 --> 00:11:49,919
<i>If Misa's put in danger,
I'll be suspected and killed.</i>

214
00:11:51,128 --> 00:11:54,590
<i>Right now, she's an even
bigger nuisance than L is.</i>

215
00:11:56,425 --> 00:11:58,093
<i>Sh-She's...</i>

216
00:11:58,802 --> 00:12:00,429
<i>She does something
this conspicuous?</i>

217
00:12:00,429 --> 00:12:01,055
MISA AMANE

218
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:03,891
<i>What'Il happen if it's discovered
that I met up with someone like this?</i>

219
00:12:04,767 --> 00:12:07,519
<i>Damn it! She's in the way
no matter how I think about it.</i>

220
00:12:07,770 --> 00:12:08,896
<i>What do I do?</i>

221
00:12:09,313 --> 00:12:14,318
<i>No... that aside, I should think
of a way to use Misa's eyes to kill L.</i>

222
00:12:15,444 --> 00:12:17,112
<i>If I just eliminate L...</i>

223
00:12:20,491 --> 00:12:22,159
Good morning, Light!

224
00:12:22,451 --> 00:12:23,535
Good morning.

225
00:12:23,744 --> 00:12:28,624
Mom, Sayu, could you keep Misa
a secret from Dad?

226
00:12:29,458 --> 00:12:30,501
All right.

227
00:12:30,751 --> 00:12:33,420
I also want you to keep it secret,
not just from Dad,

228
00:12:33,504 --> 00:12:35,172
but from everyone.

229
00:12:35,631 --> 00:12:38,050
She's an up-and-coming model,
actually,

230
00:12:38,133 --> 00:12:39,802
so it would be problematic
if people found out about us.

231
00:12:39,885 --> 00:12:41,637
What?! Is that so?

232
00:12:41,804 --> 00:12:43,973
I thought she was cute...

233
00:12:44,556 --> 00:12:49,311
Just what I'd expect for your girlfriend...
I'll keep it a secret. . .for 5,000 yen.

234
00:12:49,645 --> 00:12:50,646
Silly...

235
00:12:52,648 --> 00:12:54,525
TO-OH UNIVERSITY

236
00:12:55,776 --> 00:12:56,819
On page 246...

237
00:12:56,986 --> 00:12:59,530
<i>Misa's final message
will arrive today.</i>

238
00:13:00,447 --> 00:13:02,950
<i>Instead of going to
the television station,</i>

239
00:13:03,033 --> 00:13:05,119
<i>it should be routed to
the task force headquarters.</i>

240
00:13:06,036 --> 00:13:08,580
<i>I have to go to headquarters
in order to see L's reaction...</i>

241
00:13:08,664 --> 00:13:11,166
Yagami... Yagami...

242
00:13:12,126 --> 00:13:14,962
You told me that you'd
go outwith me, right?

243
00:13:15,504 --> 00:13:17,006
Yeah, I did.

244
00:13:17,298 --> 00:13:21,010
That's why I'm sitting next
to you at this lecture.

245
00:13:21,093 --> 00:13:22,094
Yes.

246
00:13:22,177 --> 00:13:25,055
But you don't seem happy at all.

247
00:13:25,139 --> 00:13:27,016
You've been completely
ignoring me.

248
00:13:27,516 --> 00:13:28,726
That's not true at all.

249
00:13:29,810 --> 00:13:33,397
I was just thinking about the Way
everyone's going to be talking about us.

250
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:36,942
To think that I'm going outwith you,
the famous Miss To-oh University...

251
00:13:37,401 --> 00:13:39,737
It's obvious,
you really are beautiful.

252
00:13:42,323 --> 00:13:48,412
Please don't think about such things.
I don't like being called Miss whatever.

253
00:13:48,704 --> 00:13:50,080
Yeah. You're right.

254
00:13:50,706 --> 00:13:53,167
<i>What's with this woman?
She loves it.</i>

255
00:13:54,335 --> 00:13:57,755
Miss Takada, let's just take
things at our own pace.

256
00:13:58,130 --> 00:13:59,131
Okay.

257
00:14:03,427 --> 00:14:04,428
Hello.

258
00:14:05,137 --> 00:14:07,806
Light, good timing.

259
00:14:08,474 --> 00:14:11,602
A video message from
the Second Kira just arrived.

260
00:14:12,353 --> 00:14:14,563
Another one? That was fast.

261
00:14:14,813 --> 00:14:17,566
Yes. I think this is the last one.

262
00:14:18,067 --> 00:14:19,818
Well, take a look at this.

263
00:14:21,737 --> 00:14:23,655
<i>I will stop trying to meet Kira.</i>

264
00:14:24,365 --> 00:14:27,409
<i>I'd like to thank the police
for their advice.</i>

265
00:14:28,118 --> 00:14:32,956
<i>But I'm going to help Kira
erase evil from the world...</i>

266
00:14:33,123 --> 00:14:34,708
<i>I'm going to cooperate with him
and gain his acceptance.</i>

267
00:14:35,250 --> 00:14:38,754
<i>I will begin by punishing criminals
that Kira hasn't punished yet. Also...</i>

268
00:14:39,588 --> 00:14:43,175
<i>I plan to make this world
a better place</i>

269
00:14:43,258 --> 00:14:45,511
<i>by sharing this power
among those who are worthy...</i>

270
00:14:48,222 --> 00:14:49,848
Watching this...

271
00:14:49,932 --> 00:14:53,227
makes me feel that Kira and
the Second Kira have joined forces.

272
00:14:55,104 --> 00:14:56,438
How do you know that
they've joined forces?

273
00:14:56,730 --> 00:14:58,232
Didn't you sense it?

274
00:14:59,274 --> 00:15:03,112
I thought you would
get the same impression.

275
00:15:05,531 --> 00:15:10,035
First of all, his attitude towards
meeting Kira completely changed.

276
00:15:10,744 --> 00:15:13,539
Also, he now says that he wants
to punish criminals

277
00:15:13,622 --> 00:15:16,792
that Kira didn't punish
in order to gain his acceptance.

278
00:15:18,919 --> 00:15:21,130
Why didn't he do this before?

279
00:15:21,713 --> 00:15:24,550
He probably never thought
that far ahead, so...

280
00:15:25,467 --> 00:15:28,470
It's likely that he's working with Kira,
and was told to say that.

281
00:15:29,972 --> 00:15:34,268
He was also ordered to hide
the fact that they're working together.

282
00:15:34,476 --> 00:15:35,477
I see.

283
00:15:35,978 --> 00:15:39,189
That probably means that Kira isn't
thinking about his actions very much.

284
00:15:39,523 --> 00:15:40,607
Yes.

285
00:15:42,484 --> 00:15:45,154
Did Kira encounter something
he couldn't overcome?

286
00:15:45,404 --> 00:15:48,240
He probably was trying to scare us
by making it obvious

287
00:15:48,323 --> 00:15:50,492
that he'd recruited the Second Kira.

288
00:15:50,909 --> 00:15:52,995
Their union is really threatening.

289
00:15:53,579 --> 00:15:57,541
But this lessens the suspicion
I had of Light.

290
00:15:57,749 --> 00:16:00,002
What do you mean, Ryuzaki?!

291
00:16:00,919 --> 00:16:02,421
If Light was Kira,

292
00:16:02,504 --> 00:16:05,632
then he wouldn't have sent
in a video like this.

293
00:16:05,966 --> 00:16:11,221
He would have tried to threaten me, L,
into appearing on television again.

294
00:16:12,014 --> 00:16:14,224
Maintaining that lie that
they aren't working together,

295
00:16:14,308 --> 00:16:16,852
he would have placed all
the responsibility on Second Kira...

296
00:16:18,645 --> 00:16:20,230
And this is what he'd have him say:

297
00:16:22,399 --> 00:16:24,818
"I stopped because
Kira told me to,"

298
00:16:24,902 --> 00:16:28,113
"but I don't think that warning
would come from the real Kira."

299
00:16:28,655 --> 00:16:31,116
"Kira would be happy if L died."

300
00:16:31,366 --> 00:16:33,535
"There's no way he'd stop me."

301
00:16:35,162 --> 00:16:36,163
Ryuzaki...

302
00:16:36,330 --> 00:16:37,331
Yes?

303
00:16:37,414 --> 00:16:40,626
I would never do that
if I were Kira.

304
00:16:41,168 --> 00:16:42,169
Why?

305
00:16:42,711 --> 00:16:44,671
I know your personality.

306
00:16:44,755 --> 00:16:51,470
I would never go on TV,
no matter how he was threatened.

307
00:16:52,054 --> 00:16:54,389
He wouldn't want to die
in someone else's place.

308
00:16:54,848 --> 00:16:57,309
He would think of
some way to escape.

309
00:16:58,977 --> 00:17:00,437
You figured it out.

310
00:17:00,604 --> 00:17:04,650
Light, stop saying,
"if I were Kira."

311
00:17:04,733 --> 00:17:06,401
I don't like hearing it,
even hypothetically.

312
00:17:06,527 --> 00:17:08,320
Oh, sorry, Dad...

313
00:17:09,238 --> 00:17:12,908
But I want to tell Ryuzaki
what I think.

314
00:17:13,909 --> 00:17:15,994
I have to pose the scenario
hypothetically

315
00:17:16,078 --> 00:17:18,664
in order to solve this case quickly
and to clear my name.

316
00:17:18,747 --> 00:17:23,835
Besides, it's because
I'm not Kira that I can talk in that way.

317
00:17:24,836 --> 00:17:25,879
You're right.

318
00:17:26,547 --> 00:17:28,215
You're not Kira.

319
00:17:28,423 --> 00:17:31,385
Rather, it would be a problem
if you were Kira.

320
00:17:32,219 --> 00:17:35,514
Because you're...

321
00:17:35,597 --> 00:17:38,350
my very first friend...

322
00:17:46,775 --> 00:17:50,946
Yeah, Ryuzaki, I consider you a friend too.
We have so much in common.

323
00:17:52,406 --> 00:17:53,407
Thank you.

324
00:17:55,617 --> 00:17:58,287
It's been lonely since you've been
taking breaks from school.

325
00:17:59,079 --> 00:18:01,415
I'd like to play tennis with you again.

326
00:18:02,332 --> 00:18:03,959
Yes. By all means.

327
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:17,306
Friend? Friend, huh?
Aren't you glad, Light?

328
00:18:17,806 --> 00:18:19,766
That damn Ryuzaki
immediately noticed

329
00:18:19,850 --> 00:18:22,603
the connection between
Kira and the Second Kira...

330
00:18:22,853 --> 00:18:25,480
I've got to eliminate him quickly...

331
00:18:26,189 --> 00:18:27,316
Oh I see...

332
00:18:27,482 --> 00:18:30,360
<i>This makes it all the more dangerous
for me t0 see Misa.</i>

333
00:18:30,902 --> 00:18:32,446
Light!

334
00:18:34,698 --> 00:18:36,867
I just couldn't wait
two weeks...

335
00:18:37,159 --> 00:18:39,661
I was just about to go
to your house!

336
00:18:41,163 --> 00:18:46,460
<i>T-This is the first time
I've really wanted to hit a woman...</i>

337
00:18:47,169 --> 00:18:49,671
I-| just wanted to see you
so badly...

338
00:18:50,797 --> 00:18:53,008
Well... Come over to my house.

339
00:18:53,342 --> 00:18:54,343
Okay!

340
00:18:58,347 --> 00:18:59,681
Another girl?

341
00:19:02,392 --> 00:19:06,229
Welcome, Misa! I saw you in
a whole bunch of magazines!

342
00:19:06,688 --> 00:19:07,731
Welcome.

343
00:19:08,774 --> 00:19:10,275
Sorry for the intrusion.

344
00:19:10,901 --> 00:19:12,486
Mom, please get some tea ready...

345
00:19:15,864 --> 00:19:16,907
Rem.

346
00:19:18,033 --> 00:19:20,452
You're Misa's ally, aren't you?

347
00:19:20,744 --> 00:19:25,540
Yeah. I've watched her many times
from the Shinigami Realm.

348
00:19:26,124 --> 00:19:29,211
I've developed a bit of
affection for her.

349
00:19:29,544 --> 00:19:31,588
Affection, even though
you're a Shinigami?

350
00:19:33,131 --> 00:19:35,092
You don't seem to like that

351
00:19:35,175 --> 00:19:38,261
I said that I'd kill you
if you tried to kill her.

352
00:19:38,804 --> 00:19:42,683
Does this mean that if
Misa's happy that you'll feel fine?

353
00:19:43,016 --> 00:19:45,143
Well, you could say that.

354
00:19:45,560 --> 00:19:47,688
I just don't want
to see her unhappy.

355
00:19:48,271 --> 00:19:49,564
Misa is...

356
00:19:51,817 --> 00:19:53,402
in love with me.

357
00:19:53,527 --> 00:19:54,528
Light...

358
00:19:54,903 --> 00:19:55,904
Misa.

359
00:19:55,987 --> 00:19:56,988
Yes?

360
00:19:57,072 --> 00:20:00,033
Would my happiness
make you happy?

361
00:20:00,575 --> 00:20:01,576
Yes.

362
00:20:02,911 --> 00:20:06,248
Then could you ask Rem
to kill L?

363
00:20:07,541 --> 00:20:10,001
Rem wants you to be happy.

364
00:20:10,168 --> 00:20:14,756
If L catches one of us,
we'll both be unhappy.

365
00:20:16,758 --> 00:20:21,221
A Shinigami can't tell a person's name
to someone who has a notebook,

366
00:20:21,346 --> 00:20:24,850
but there's no restriction
against Rem killing anyone.

367
00:20:24,933 --> 00:20:30,689
Yeah. If you kill L,
I think I can love Misa more

368
00:20:30,772 --> 00:20:32,399
and I would be very grateful.

369
00:20:32,607 --> 00:20:34,943
Above all, it'll make us both happy.

370
00:20:35,652 --> 00:20:36,653
Rem...

371
00:20:37,112 --> 00:20:40,907
I want Light to love me.
Light and I will be grateful.

372
00:20:41,283 --> 00:20:43,326
That would be. . .my happiness.

373
00:20:55,255 --> 00:20:56,256
Fine.

374
00:20:57,674 --> 00:21:02,053
Fine, Light Yagami.
I don't like you.

375
00:21:02,304 --> 00:21:06,141
Even if this ends up lengthening
your lifespan, I won't die.

376
00:21:06,892 --> 00:21:08,769
I'll kill L for you.

377
00:21:09,478 --> 00:21:12,773
I means nothing to me.

378
00:21:13,148 --> 00:21:14,649
All right!

379
00:21:14,816 --> 00:21:16,818
Thank you, Rem!

380
00:21:17,152 --> 00:21:18,987
That's my Rem!

381
00:21:20,322 --> 00:21:21,615
<i>I will die,</i>

382
00:21:22,741 --> 00:21:23,909
<i>this easily?</i>

383
00:21:24,951 --> 00:21:28,789
TO BE CONTINUED

384
00:21:29,206 --> 00:21:34,294
<i>I dreamed a dream
that no one could see,</i>

385
00:21:34,377 --> 00:21:39,674
<i>I threw away everything
that I didn't need</i>

386
00:21:40,008 --> 00:21:43,220
<i>I'm holding these feelings</i>

387
00:21:43,303 --> 00:21:48,683
<i>That I can't give up in my heart</i>

388
00:21:48,850 --> 00:21:55,106
<i>Even if my feet fall victim
to the shackles of sacrifice</i>

389
00:21:55,190 --> 00:21:59,694
<i>In between reality and my ideal</i>

390
00:22:00,487 --> 00:22:05,367
<i>I can't hold back
the flooding impulses</i>

391
00:22:05,534 --> 00:22:09,079
<i>Because I have a strong desire</i>

392
00:22:09,162 --> 00:22:12,833
<i>To accomplish</i>

393
00:22:13,416 --> 00:22:18,004
<i>[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]</i>

394
00:22:18,129 --> 00:22:23,718
<i>I'm not weak enough to believe</i>

395
00:22:23,802 --> 00:22:28,723
<i>Any of these negative perceptions</i>

396
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:34,062
<i>I'm a trickster
who doesn't know solitude</i>

397
00:22:38,775 --> 00:22:40,443
PREVIEW

398
00:22:40,443 --> 00:22:43,446
That's right. Since Ryuga's revealed
that he's L, I must kill him.

399
00:22:43,655 --> 00:22:45,115
This is all a wager now.

400
00:22:46,408 --> 00:22:49,995
Tomorrow will be L's,
no Ryuga/Ryuzaki's,

401
00:22:50,036 --> 00:22:51,371
.“finalday.

402
00:22:51,872 --> 00:22:53,790
NEXT EPISODE: WAGER

